    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Amelii </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> Multiplici laborum merito <lb n="2"/>varioque voluptatum <lb n="3"/>genere stimulantibus <lb n="4"/>paternis aviti<surplus>i</surplus>s etiam <lb n="5"/>documentis ab ineun<lb break="no" n="6"/>te aetate patriam cives<lb break="no" n="7"/>que suos promerenti <lb n="8"/><expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arco</ex></expan> Vibio An<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>iano</abbr></expan> Gemino <lb n="9"/><expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>iro</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>erfectissimo</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>fla</abbr><ex>mini</ex></expan> p<expan><ex>er</ex><abbr>p</abbr><ex>etuo</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>pont</abbr><ex>ifici</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>sacerdotal</abbr><ex>i</ex></expan> <lb n="10"/>provinciae Tripolitanae <lb n="11"/>bis <expan><abbr>IIvir</abbr><ex>o</ex></expan> ex sufragio <lb n="12"/>quietissimi populi et de<lb break="no" n="13"/>creto splendidissimi ordinis
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>The inscription is carved over an erased earlier text. Interpunktion: Palmette. Datierung: spätkonstantinische Zeit.</p>
            </div>
